t7.expressions

Class BooleanExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • t7.expressions.BooleanExpression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Expression

    public class BooleanExpression
extends java.lang.Object
implements Expression
    Represents a Boolean Expression, it could be a single value, or a variable, or a binary expression. Binary expression could be a boolean expression between two boolean expressions, or could be two arithemtic expressions with a comparator.
    Author:
    kinan
